## Advanced Google Dorking Queries for LinkedIn Remote Cybersecurity Positions with Recruiter Contact Information

### General Remote Cybersecurity Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("cybersecurity" OR "infosec" OR "cyber security analyst") AND ("remote hiring" OR "remote position" OR "work remotely") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "contact me" OR "@gmail.com") AND ("remote" OR "WFH" OR "work from home")
```

### Remote SOC Analyst & Network Security Positions
```
site:linkedin.com ("SOC analyst" OR "security operations center analyst") AND ("actively recruiting remotely" OR "remote positions") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "direct contact") AND ("remote" OR "telecommute" OR "fully remote")
```

### Remote Threat Hunting & Cyber Threat Intelligence (CTI)
```
site:linkedin.com ("threat hunting" OR "cyber threat intelligence" OR "threat analyst") AND ("remote hiring" OR "remote roles available") AND ("email" OR "phone number" OR "contact info") AND ("remote" OR "virtual" OR "distributed team")
```

### Remote Penetration Testing & Ethical Hacking
```
site:linkedin.com ("penetration tester" OR "red team" OR "ethical hacker") AND ("remote positions" OR "remote roles open") AND ("email" OR "direct contact" OR "phone number") AND ("remote" OR "work remotely" OR "telework")
```

### Remote Incident Response & Digital Forensics
```
site:linkedin.com ("incident response" OR "digital forensics" OR "DFIR") AND ("actively recruiting remotely" OR "remote jobs available") AND ("email address" OR "phone" OR "contact me directly") AND ("remote" OR "virtual" OR "WFH")
```

### Remote Government & Defense Cybersecurity Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("government cybersecurity" OR "federal cybersecurity" OR "defense cyber") AND ("remote hiring" OR "telework positions") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "@gov") AND ("remote" OR "telecommute" OR "virtual")
```

### Remote Incident Response Analyst Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("incident response analyst" OR "digital forensics") AND ("remote hiring" OR "urgent remote positions") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "direct contact") AND ("remote" OR "work remotely" OR "WFH")
```

### Remote Entry-Level Cybersecurity & Internships
```
site:linkedin.com ("entry-level cybersecurity" OR "junior cyber analyst" OR "cyber internship") AND ("remote roles" OR "apply remotely") AND ("email" OR "phone number" OR "reach me") AND ("remote" OR "work from anywhere" OR "WFH")
```

### Remote Cybersecurity Consultancy Roles
```
site:linkedin.com ("cybersecurity consultant" OR "infosec consultant") AND ("remote consultancy" OR "consulting remotely") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "contact directly") AND ("remote" OR "virtual" OR "telecommute")
```

### Remote Cybersecurity Training & Instructor Positions
```
site:linkedin.com ("cybersecurity instructor" OR "infosec trainer") AND ("remote training roles" OR "instructor remote positions") AND ("email" OR "phone" OR "contact me") AND ("remote" OR "online teaching" OR "virtual instructor")
```

